{"tid":1936523,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"大量親共派文宣出現於元朗連儂牆 防暴警員於附近戒備","createTime":"2020-03-21T09:29:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-21T13:48:20.000Z","uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"1b2cfca0c897e4f9211aa1ca76a3d181e96e2c2e","tid":1936523,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T09:29:23.000Z","msg":"Stand News 立場新聞<br />\n<br />\n今日是元朗 721 襲擊事件八個月，網上流傳有人號召今晚「清除黃屍曱甴」。在元朗西鐵站外的連儂牆，今日出現大量批評示威者的文宣。其中有署名「香港市民」的文宣，批評「暴徒」破壞香港和平繁榮；有人貼上民主黨議員林卓廷的照片，指控他導致 721 事件。現場亦有文宣要求政府盡快就《基本法》22條立法。<br />\n<br />\n有防暴警員在連儂牆附近戒備，但未有清理牆上的文宣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3jGoPRQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3jGoPRQ.jpg&h=4d4e49ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/photos/a.720050934747196/2942328005852800/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fphotos%2Fa.720050934747196%2F2942328005852800%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=KoefzaQlkmro%2FPgOzv92FyKjAP3shAOQj%2BHHIi00eAs%3D&h=eed9c770\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/photos/a.720050934747196/2942328005852800/?type=3&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"ff99e7350f65565a07f3428645cb2ca1ca42895c","tid":1936523,"uid":112581,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"1b2cfca0c897e4f9211aa1ca76a3d181e96e2c2e","tid":1936523,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T09:29:23.000Z","msg":"Stand News 立場新聞<br />\n<br />\n今日是元朗 721 襲擊事件八個月，網上流傳有人號召今晚「清除黃屍曱甴」。在元朗西鐵站外的連儂牆，今日出現大量批評示威者的文宣。其中有署名「香港市民」的文宣，批評「暴徒」破壞香港和平繁榮；有人貼上民主黨議員林卓廷的照片，指控他導致 721 事件。現場亦有文宣要求政府盡快就《基本法》22條立法。<br />\n<br />\n有防暴警員在連儂牆附近戒備，但未有清理牆上的文宣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3jGoPRQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3jGoPRQ.jpg&h=4d4e49ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/photos/a.7200